&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;While performing the duties of this job, the employee is frequently required to stand, walk, use hands and fingers, handle or feel, reach with hands and arms, climb or balance, stoop, kneel, crouch, or crawl and talk and hear.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The employee must occasionally lift and/or move up to 45 pounds.&lt;/li&gt;
